General.Name: UIE PLC
General.Description: UIE PLC invests in the agro-industrial sector, and industrial and technology businesses. The company primarily cultivates oil palm and coconuts, and processes palm oil. It operates in Malaysia, Indonesia, the United States, Europe, and internationally. The company was formerly known as United International Enterprises Limited and changed its name to UIE PLC in October 2020. The company was founded in 1906 and is headquartered in Ta' Xbiex, Malta. UIE PLC is a subsidiary of Brothers Holding Limited.
